\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbc958fff4821b519aa2fdc971963b28d38a3bb","tid":169733,"uid":64787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果陣係打上現職公司既mpf公司 hxbx黎<br />\n話想做整合 佢會問你邊間有acc<br />\n咁來來去去都係x利 x明架啦<br />\n大不了打去白撞check自己id有冇acc.<br />\n<br />\n跟手hxbx會同你駁條三奶去果幾間公司問<br />\n你對完身份 hxbx會幫你問<br />\n查到有佢會mark低 再下一間<br />\n果陣hxbx就幫我填晒d轉移form 寄俾我簽名 再寄返俾佢<br />\n搞掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實點解你地會覺得電話打嚟打去 會方便既呢 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n一個人全部 MPF account 都喺 積金局有哂資料 <br />\n申請一份 history 又唔駛錢 , 等一星期左右就有哂資料畀返你 <br />\n一目瞭然 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   走去信埋 D 服務商 hotline <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個電話炸喎<br />\n佢會駁線搞架啦<br />\n最重要唔洗自己填 唔洗怕填錯 到時補黎補去仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋年中收咁多手續費 唔洗佢做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都prefer 自已打理返D ACC好D<br />\n硬係覺得D 基金佬信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞掂晒會有封確認信俾你核對架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢幫你填只係假手於人 <br />\nfinal 自己都有責任確認多次先簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係想講 唔係個個人都有時間親手填 寄 再等收信 再搵轉移form<br />\n好費時架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44a3444b585db5478831487c73f90346df88b87","tid":169733,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你係 80  90 後 ,  好心你地就管理下你 D 強積金啦 , <br />\n<br />\n錢嚟架<br />\n<br />\n咪撚聽 D ON 9 講,  咩強姦金一定蝕  依 D ON 9 野先得架 <br />\n<br />\n你儲左一筆錢,  人地幫你投資 ,  你 Set 好 D PLAN ,  一定有賺架喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似今日年頭至依家,  某類基金 已經升左成 7 - 8 %  <br />\n依 D 錢 係要執架啦,  如果唔係點滾大佢 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該用邊間去做整合好?<br />\n同埋而加22歲 後生 點揀D組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前亂9填晒D高風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我既意思係,   D 乜鳩整合   係呃鳩你幫襯佢架咋   <br />\n一般人都可以  自己做整合,   只係你地平時懶, 唔想理 MPF 啫 <br />\n<br />\n你做左野幾多年 ?  一般嚟講 後生可以揀高風險既基金,  但其實 「高風險」依個字又係誤導人 。  依家 D MPF 服務商已經有 網上管理系統<br />\n<br />\n例如 你揀左 「高風險」既股票基金,   但有日你留意到外圍股市開始跌啦喎,  咪上網  轉返  靠安全既組合囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本就係當股票咁玩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己錢自己管"},{"pid":"14b7157ca834e783bbfe4fe5df1b3a3d2abe349e","tid":169733,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞掂晒會有封確認信俾你核對架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢幫你填只係假手於人 <br />\nfinal 自己都有責任確認多次先簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係想講 唔係個個人都有時間親手填 寄 再等收信 再搵轉移form<br />\n好費時架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMPF 係自己既財產,  自己掌握返個流程,  其實唔係應該架咩 ? <br />\n<br />\n正如當初 迷你債券爆,  咪就係一班人  又係假手於人, <br />\n<br />\n最終到爆煲之後先嚟發覺原來自己投資乜都唔知 ?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話 唔畀保險 D 人幫,   但質素同誠意都唔該好少少呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己掌握返個 MPF 流程有好處,  點解?  <br />\n因為可以上網自己揀想做參襯邊間 MPF 服務商囉<br />\n<br />\n好似 樓上個位 AXX ,  佢 D 基金今年至今都跑輸同行啦,  憑咩去叫人轉去先 ?<br />\n<br />\n咪就係搏香港人 乜春都唔想理,  搵水魚囉<br />\n<br />\nMPF 服務商 表現 可以喺下列網址睇到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae5effe86bbec2b08b45454edcff262f9d31507","tid":169733,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本就係當股票咁玩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己錢自己管</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nexact7ly ,    仲有,  班保險 Sales ,  話就話幫你免費整合 MPF,<br />\n<br />\n之後呢 ?  係呀  D MPF 係整合左<br />\n<br />\n但 D 人根本唔知揀咩基金好,  日後點管理好 <br />\n<br />\n個班 sales , 幫你整合完,  就拍拍屁股交人頭數啦<br />\n<br />\n會理你 ?  得,  你要用佢其他收費項目囉"},{"pid":"9eaecdfcfcea909c84c3426a41b2d27a63321aa2","tid":169733,"uid":64787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"講講下我都想run一次 d plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好似冇申請網上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42287f5a8bf1994b7e489af001d710afef3be8e","tid":169733,"uid":3930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2c478e817285a60c9d2957a344f436cb6ffef73","tid":169733,"uid":3930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但我已經唔記得有幾多份mpf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁估計有成4-5份<br />\n完全唔知點入手<br />\n應該點搞好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"7181f8447eeac569aec704d40da95ef8fa8457da","tid":169733,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"搭單一開，我衣家間公司係玩公積金，咁我可唔可以將之前d強積金轉埋入去個公積金戶口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15c4aaf9f1ac5546b362e3b4f92116b577f9435","tid":169733,"uid":58249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,